Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.99,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Isn't that something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.06,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,The first batter up,\Nand in the major league, too!
