Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.93,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Are you living your life\Nto write an autobiography?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.37,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Of course not. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）そんなわけじゃ\Nないけどさ… でもさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:33.94,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy life! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しい人生 送ろーぜ！ ほらっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）えっ？ おい 田辺～っ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:34.97,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子部員１）\Nもー 吉田(よしだ)君ったら！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.04,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,-C'mon, Yoshida-kun!\N-Have you gained weight, Kazuko?
