Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子部員４）キャーッ\Nかけないでよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.85,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Don't splash me!
